              <hi rend="i">MLA 1983</hi>
            </title>
          </head>
          <p>Mark Greenberg is preparing a proposal for a special session celebrating the bicentennial of 
<hi rend="i">Poetical Sketches</hi> at the 1983 MLA Convention in New York. Space for one or two papers remains,
and he invites proposals from interested readers, including (and perhaps even especially) graduate students.
Please write him at the Department of Humanities, Drexel University, Philadelphia, PA 19104.</p>
